Package com.samysadi.acs.user

This package contains definitions for user entities of the simulator.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ThinClient
    This interface describes a thin client.
    It is used by users to have access to the Cloud and use its resources.
    ThinClientVirtualMachine
    A thin client VM is different from regular VMs because you cannot allocate some resources types for it (virtual ram, virtual storage, processing units).
    If you try to allocate such resources you will get an UnsupportedOperationException.
    User
    A user is a simulation entity that utilizes Cloud resources.
    It owns a set of VMs and storage Files.
